The Soothe 'n Groove Mobile is a melodious and colorful mobile that offers a world of music to your child. It has 18 different tunes in 6 separate categories, which is up to 40 minutes of continuous non-repetitive music. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.
